cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.LG 

This paper is about image matting, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach is specifically designed for portrait images, which suggests that it may also fall under the sub-category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of a mobile device for real-time processing suggests that it may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the use of deep learning in the proposed approach suggests that it may also be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG).
